= Internal Security

Lachaven, by far one of the most developed and important cities in Sordland, is governed by our party, with support from the Bludish party. It is the most stable and democratic city in Sordland, led by the able Adrian Derrow.

Our policies here affect not only the city proper, but also Sordland as a whole, as it is the commercial and economic heart of the nation - where news, achievements, and gossip spread like wildfire

